rows.label: qev030606_MSG0010
rows.name:
You are strong. Very strong.
It has been long since I enjoyed such challenge.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0011
rows.name: You remind me how it felt to march into battle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0012
rows.name:
I dodged bullets. Pierced enemy lines.
Toppled generals. All to defend my clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0013
rows.name:
But I wasn't able to save my family from Cavern Clan.
Not all of them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0014
rows.name:
I lost my wife. Daughter. Son.
Now only Bazis remains.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0015
rows.name:
With each loss, I swore to grow stronger.
To hone my edge. Protect what remained.
But in end, I could not defeat Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0016
rows.name:
I hope Nemard finds strength he needs.
Strength to protect his family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev030606_MSG0018
rows.name:
They will be wanting to begin rite of marriage.
I should return.[ST:wait ]
